分例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係成間員工都係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:52:18.000Z","msg":"老細免費提供＿＿放題<br />\n緊係食到懞左啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:53:39.000Z","msg":"我極度懷疑精神分裂會傳染，"},{"pid":"cf77340d73551f840ee93ca642072131dedafa1a","tid":1224033,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0R4d4q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0R4d4q.png&h=dbe25b0d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}